LABEL : START
COMMENT : Launch the VoIP softphone from its default installation folder.
FILE OPEN : C:\Program Files\VoIP Softphone\VoIPSoftphone.exe
COMMENT : Wait for the softphone window to be available before dialing.
WAIT FOR WINDOW : *VoIP Softphone*
COMMENT : Activate the softphone window before sending dial input.
ACTIVATE WINDOW : *VoIP Softphone*
COMMENT : Dial the QA test line (EDIT ONLY THIS NUMBER IF NEEDED).
TYPE TEXT : 786-948-1567
KEYBOARD : {ENTER}
COMMENT : Wait exactly 4500 ms after call connects.
DELAY : 4500
COMMENT : Play the desktop audio file using its absolute path.
FILE OPEN : C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Desktop\aventura_obsesion.wav
COMMENT : Hang up the current call cleanly.
KEYBOARD : ^+h
COMMENT : Immediately restart the macro loop.
GOTO : START
